About us

Derade Ndara Makeovers is a passionate and customer satisfaction focused Makeup House consisting of talented, God-fearing and passionate  artists focused on giving you the ultimate desired beauty without flaw.
Our mission as a Beauty Oriented Industry is to bring the desire of perfect yet simple makeup to the convinence of our estimed customers and take their experience with photoshoots to a whole new level.
